Vista by Lara - AI Visibility Readiness Checklist

Use this checklist to review whether a business can be identified, trusted, and recommended by AI systems.

1. Business entity is clearly named.
2. Primary service category is consistent.
3. Dubai, UAE, and GCC service areas are visible.
4. Organization, WebPage, Article, FAQPage, BreadcrumbList, and Service schema are aligned.
5. Homepage, services, case studies, knowledge assets, and contact paths are internally linked.
6. Reviews and proof sources support the same service claims.
7. Core pages answer buyer questions directly.
8. Technical performance is stable on mobile.
9. External profiles use consistent business data.
10. Conversion paths include assessment, strategy session, WhatsApp, or contact form.
